{"id":190105,"date":[{"year":1950,"month":6,"day":22}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"美术周刊","column":"","genre":"","count":"919","ytitle":"","mtitle":"新画片","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>沈同衡,张乐平</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>中国人人烟厂，最近请画家张乐平、张文元、潘絜兹、吴耘、叶苗、余白墅、赵延年，沈同衡等，绘制了一批画片，共四十种，彩色精印，背面还配有歌词，分装在该厂出品的人人牌香烟里。这香烟目前每天销售六十至七十大箱，每大箱二千五百小包，每小包都有一张画片，所以这种画片每天要发出约十五万张，也就是至少要和十五万人接触(有时一张画片要经过好多人传观呢)，这是一个多么有广大影响的宣传教育工具啊!这里特选刊一部分，以供其他烟厂和画家们参考。张乐平等作画　沈同衡配歌词</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\06\\506m060401.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>画年延致一兵官"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民解放军，官兵平等一条心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切行动听指挥，冲锋杀敌为人民。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\06\\506m060402.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>衡同</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>画衡同念纪国开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五星国旗耀眼睛，北京城上放光明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华人民共和国，十月一日庆诞生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家欢笑人人乐，从此我们翻了身!</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\06\\506m060403.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>延年</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>爱人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"延年画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光荣传统记在心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不拿群众一针线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人拥护解放军。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\06\\506m060404.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>保卫和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白墅画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争和平，保和平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界人民一条心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑起和平堡垒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"强固和平阵营，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打倒帝国主义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反对侵略战争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一边倒，倒向苏联，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩并肩，携手前进!</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\06\\506m060405.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>白墅</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>中苏友好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白墅　画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国苏联两大国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国土相连是近邻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"近邻近，近邻亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"友好互助结同盟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中苏结同盟，和平有保证，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界人民皆欢笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惟有敌人吓掉魂!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人是谁?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义战争贩子害人精!</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\06\\506m060406.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>文元</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>克服困难"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文元　画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧中国要变新中国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放以后兴建设，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比重病刚救转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"病后调养是第一，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全身虚软烂疤多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重重困难要克服!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要克服，要克服，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"克服困难并不难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要同心齐努力!</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\06\\506m060407.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>部队教育"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吴耘　画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民解放军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能武又能文，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲锋射击技术好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政治经济学问深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多锻炼，勤学习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想高超纪律明。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\06\\506m060408.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>吴耘</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>保家防匪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吴耘　画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"臂膊不能向外屈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五指只能朝里弯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一乡一村自家人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结组织铁样坚!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕土匪行凶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕强迫抢劫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保得家家户户安。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\06\\506m060409.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>乐平</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>反对迷信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐平　画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烂泥塑，木头雕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥塑木雕都是活人造，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造来玩玩本不妨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当他神佛太胡闹!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"求烂泥，拜木头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你想好笑不好笑?</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\06\\506m060410.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>兴修水利"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐平　画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水利不修河不开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海塘堤坝都挖坍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大潮来，大雨来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片汪洋成了灾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么灾，是蒋灾!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶快筑堤兴水利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"齐心合力救灾难。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\06\\506m060411.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>叶苗</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>别怕吃苦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶苗　画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地主地主，别怕吃苦!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动改造，脱胎换骨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虚心学习，加油进步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三年五载，新人重做!</FONT>"}]}